  chapter: 8
  title: TBA
  story: "You approach a glowing cosmic rift where space ripples like waves in water.
    Light pulses in patterns that twist your ship\u2019s sensors. Gizmo warns the
    energy here is unstable.\n\nInside the rift, oscillations slam your spacecraft,
    throwing it off balance. Electromagnetic waves disrupt your controls, shaking
    the vehicle violently.\n\nYou study the shifting frequencies around you and adjust
    your systems to match. By syncing with the rift\u2019s wave patterns, the turbulence
    begins to calm.\n\nThe rift releases you in a final burst of energy, launching
    you above a blue water planet. You\u2019ve survived by mastering waves and oscillations,
    ready for the next challenge."
